                                    </div>
                                    <div class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white">
                                        <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-pale ring-1 ring-brand-soft"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-brand-navy/70"><span class="font-medium text-brand-navy">V5</span> new feature.</p>
                                    <time datetime="2023-01-23T10:32" class="flex-none py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-brand-navy/60">10d ago</time>
                                </li>
